Importance Sampling
Extension of rejection sampling without requiring “rejection”:

Draw samples from importance distribution g(x);
Reweight samples: \[
\begin{align*}
\mathbb{E}_f[h(x)] &= \int_x \frac{f(x)}{g(x)} g(x)h(x) dx \\
&\approx \frac{1}{M} \sum_{i=1}^M \frac{f(x)}{g(x)}h(x)
\end{align*}
\]

